txt.en: Milonnen can be found in Ost Anglebed in north-central Lebennin.\n\nYou have defeated the drake, Render, and should now report your success to Milonnen.
Talk to Milonnen in Ost Anglebed
Roving Threat: Render, Shadow of the White Mountains
The drake, Render, has come down from the White Mountains, striking greater fear into the already terrified people of Lebennin.
'You did well to cut down that drake, for his presence filled many of our folk with dread, [placeholder].\n\n'I am certain it was no simple task, so take this as your reward.'
Render can be found somewhere in Lebennin.\n\nMilonnen has asked you to track and defeat the drake, Render.

'I have received word of a great drake that has come down from the mountains.

'It is said that he has preyed only on our goats so far, but such a beast is beyond our control and may soon bring further ruin to our lands.

'Seek him out and defeat him, [placeholder], before he can set flame to any of our settlements that the Corsairs and Haradrim spared. A drake of his size should not be difficult to track....'
